{"tid":985584,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟統計下大家飲奶蓋茶嘅習慣","createTime":"2019-01-17T17:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T02:30:30.000Z","uid":948,"like":62,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30bb571133fb93f1eafa53c08a440446abdcd3a3","tid":985584,"uid":948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"今日排緊沙田HEYTEA嗰陣<br />\n發現好多人都唔識奶蓋茶嘅飲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奶蓋個texture同杯茶係完全唔同<br />\n最佳嘅飲法一定係唔用飲筒沿住邊飲 <br />\n一啖濃厚嘅奶蓋 一啖茶澀<br />\n係感受緊杯嘢嘅層次<br />\n<br />\n但見好多人都係打完卡<br />\n直接用飲筒攪勻飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣唔係毀咗杯奶蓋茶咩<br />\n不如直接買杯奶茶好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奶蓋層次示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wddxb.com/uploads/allimg/180225/1-1P2250955594J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wddxb.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F180225%2F1-1P2250955594J.png&h=437906dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攪勻飲示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.prjk.com/uploads/180930/7_211713_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prjk.com%2Fuploads%2F180930%2F7_211713_1.png&h=01009bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攪勻飲除咗破壞層次 仲破壞埋個茶底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想知大家係咪都習慣整到佢好似洗米水咁飲<br />\n<br />\n飲層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲洗米水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ea1e6975bfa94f8a146286fb7d2545b6c4ec5c","tid":985584,"uid":2148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常個店員唔會教你飲架咩"},{"pid":"ee4fdaf5cad43146fdbab1fc594566973511bb29","tid":985584,"uid":948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"42ea1e6975bfa94f8a146286fb7d2545b6c4ec5c","tid":985584,"uid":2148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常個店員唔會教你飲架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"店員都係話沿邊飲先感受到層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7b146f76cf5d5cd6f75d11ef4f952948be634f","tid":985584,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"直插最底飲啲勉強叫做入得口嘅茶，飲到層奶就掉因為真係好難飲"},{"pid":"868ae0fb3c2331791fdeac519ac6c4eb208ea161","tid":985584,"uid":109531,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"負皮係比喜茶同樓主條撚樣"},{"pid":"bc3041c39cb75cadd068b3c46d0187f629505b88","tid":985584,"uid":200159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80ece2523885daf48d0d03f4c490d988242bc3d1","tid":985584,"uid":137921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"屎茶"},{"pid":"75975be96ba7e5654c8ab1b75db5b1aa20acaa6d","tid":985584,"uid":213894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c7b146f76cf5d5cd6f75d11ef4f952948be634f","tid":985584,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"直插最底飲啲勉強叫做入得口嘅茶，飲到層奶就掉因為真係好難飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔走奶蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 師兄未飲過定錢多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4cbe2d0d792942654ff27a61dea261f37ab4e0","tid":985584,"uid":230307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"食乜撚嘢喜茶吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c62e9f1fa9498ffe07ce22698cb037c5196e65d","tid":985584,"uid":182325,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"on9 飲L到你糖尿病呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid